  "instructions": [
    "Heat coconut oil in a large pot over medium heat until melted.",
    "Add diced red bell pepper and sauté until softened, about 3 minutes.",
    "Stir in frozen and fresh corn kernels, cooking for 2 minutes to release steam.",
    "Pour in vegetable broth and coconut milk, then bring to a gentle simmer.",
    "Season with salt, pepper, and lime juice, letting flavors meld for 6 minutes.",
    "Add fresh spinach and cook, stirring, until wilted, about 2 minutes.",
    "Remove from heat and stir in chopped cilantro for a bright finish.",
    "Ladle into bowls and serve immediately for a tangy, crunchy chowder."
